  "title": "Assistant Quality Assurance Manager  [WCNH]",
  "description": "<p><p>Managed <strong>quality and food safety operations</strong> within the Central Kitchen to ensure consistent and compliant product output.</p></p><p><p>Ensured all products adhered to <strong>internal quality standards</strong> as well as applicable <strong>regulatory and statutory requirements</strong>.</p></p><p><p>Developed, reviewed, and maintained <strong>food safety and quality assurance policies, procedures, and documentation</strong>.</p></p><p><p>Carried out <strong>regular inspections, hygiene checks, and internal audits</strong> to maintain high quality standards.</p></p><p><p>Evaluated and improved existing <strong>quality control processes</strong> to enhance efficiency and effectiveness.</p></p><p><p>Investigated <strong>quality-related customer complaints</strong>, identified root causes, and implemented corrective and preventive actions.</p></p><p><p>Ensured production processes complied with <strong>approved QA specifications and control measures</strong>.</p></p><p><p>Monitored adherence to <strong>standard operating procedures (SOPs)</strong> across all production activities.</p></p><p><p>Tracked and analysed <strong>product quality performance</strong> to ensure consistency and continuous improvement.</p></p><p><p>Ensured full compliance with <strong>HACCP requirements and AVA/NEA food safety regulations</strong>.</p></p><p><p>Supervised and coordinated <strong>QA team activities</strong>, providing guidance, training, and support.</p></p><p><p>Supported <strong>product development and process improvement initiatives</strong>, including R&D testing and sensory evaluations.</p></p><p><p>Assisted in the development of <strong>new products and production methods</strong> to improve quality and efficiency.</p></p><p><p>Performed other <strong>ad-hoc quality and operational tasks</strong> as directed by senior management.<br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p></p>",
